public class AdministrationInterface
extends IEpicServiceAdministrationInterface.Stub
implements org.mobilesynergies.epic.client.PresenceCallback

This is the administration interface of the epic service. It provides methods for - service configuration, - service availability, - epic network exploration, - remote command execution - stopping the service

Execute a remote command.

Specified by:
executeRemoteCommand in interface IEpicServiceAdministrationInterface
Parameters:
epicNode - The node that executes the command
command - The name of the command
sessionId - The sessionId of this command. If null a new command is created.
parametersIn - The parameters for the command of null if no parameters are known or needed
parametersOut - The parameters that are needed for completion of the next stage of the command. The caller must provide an empty ParameterMap here to receive the necessary parameters.
Returns:
The sessionId of this command. This id is used to later refer to this command.
